      "summary": "@@SITE_MD_BEGIN\n# Daily Risk Intel Digest — 2026-03-05\n\n## Highlights (10-20)\n- Solana DeFi平台Step Finance遭 Treasury攻击，损失$27M，代币价格暴跌80%+（https://www.coindesk.com/business/2026/01/31/solana-based-defi-platform-step-finance-hit-by-usd30-million-treasury-hack-as-token-price-craters）\n- Unleash Protocol遭治理攻击，损失$3.9M，资金通过Tornado Cash转移（https://www.coindesk.com/business/2025/12/30/unleash-protocol-hit-by-usd3-9-million-exploit-with-funds-routed-through-tornado-cash）\n- 冒用Circle品牌的假平台声称提供代币化黄金/白银互换服务（https://www.coindesk.com/web3/2025/12/24/circle-platform-promising-tokenized-gold-silver-swaps-is-fake-company-says）\n- Polymarket用户账户遭入侵，疑为第三方登录工具Magic Labs漏洞（https://www.coindesk.com/business/2025/12/24/polymarket-points-to-third-party-login-tool-after-users-report-account-breaches）\n- 加密用户遭\"地址投毒\"诈骗，损失$5000万（https://www.coindesk.com/web3/2025/12/20/crypto-user-loses-usd50-million-in-address-poisoning-scam）\n- 深度伪造威胁成为加密行业2026年首要安全挑战（https://www.coindesk.com/opinion/2025/12/16/the-deepfake-reckoning-why-crypto-s-next-security-battle-will-be-against-synthetic-humans）\n- 西班牙破获加密绑架团伙，物理攻击提取钱包访问权限案件增多（https://www.coindesk.com/coindesk-news/2025/12/14/spanish-authorities-bust-crypto-kidnapping-ring-after-deadly-attack）\n- 2025年社交工程诈骗成为加密领域首要威胁，技术钱包黑客占33.7%（https://www.coindesk.com/web3/2025/10/30/social-engineering-scams-top-crypto-threats-in-2025-whitebit）\n- Monero遭遇史上最深度区块链重组，118笔交易被撤销（https://www.coindesk.com/web3/2025/09/15/monero-suffers-deepest-ever-blockchain-reorganization-invalidating-118-transactions）\n- Revolut提交美国银行牌照申请，拟提供Fedwire和ACH直接接入（https://www.coindesk.com/policy/2026/03/05/crypto-friendly-fintech-giant-revolut-files-for-u-s-banking-license）\n\n## Signals & Controls\n- **Signal:** DeFi协议Treasury攻击频发，智能合约风险持续存在 → **Control:** 部署多签Treasury方案，实施tx whitelist限制，建立异常大额转出实时告警\n- **Signal:** 钓鱼/社交工程诈骗仍是主要攻击向量，占比超66% → **Control:** 用户教育+交易前地址校验强制确认，部署邮件/社交媒体钓鱼监测\n- **Signal:** 冒名品牌诈骗（Circle假平台）出现 → **Control:** 官方渠道验证机制，社群监控假冒账号，建立项目方官方声明索引\n- **S